text_JP: パルミア王立士官宿舎
真夜中から宵まで、奴は見張っているぞ
text: From midnight till dusk, he watches.

text_JP: 慈愛の女神オディナの犠牲を讃えて
text: In honor of the sacrifices of Odina, the Goddess of Compassion

text_JP: かたつむりの反乱により現在休園中
text: The park is temporarily closed due to snail rebellion.

text_JP: 温泉で「休憩」すれば、心も体もほっこり
text: Take a "Rest" at the hot spring to warm you from the inside out!
